    "Hemant Taneja is CEO of $36 billion (assets under management) venture capital firm General Catalyst.",
    "Under his leadership, GC completed mergers with European VC firm La Famiglia in 2023 and India-based VC firm Venture Highway in 2024. GC also raised $8 billion in new capital in 2024.",
