    "Since joining GC in 2001 and becoming CEO in 2021, Taneja has launched a West Coast office for the Cambridge, Massachusetts-based firm and expanded it into wealth management and buyouts.",
    "Born in Delhi, Taneja immigrated to the U.S. at age 15. He sold his first company, wireless app maker Isovia to JP Mobile after dropping out of his MIT PhD program."
